  "body": "<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Items Reworked</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">This <strong>resource pack</strong> for <strong>Minecraft Java Edition</strong> <strong>slightly enhances the textures of many in-game items</strong>, giving them a <strong>cleaner and more polished look</strong> while staying true to the vanilla style.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">✨ <strong>Note:</strong> This pack is <strong>still in development</strong>, and more item textures will be improved in future updates.</p>\n<!-- Credits above images, aligned left -->\n<div style=\"text-align: left; margin-bottom: 10px;\"><strong>Credits -</strong><br>Few textures are inspired by different packs<br>Bow - <a href=\"https://www.planetminecraft.com/member/haisuki/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Haisuki</a></div>\n<!-- Images -->\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/null/description_6cf1d258-bf00-4c72-a850-adc3b3e4f4c4.jpg\" alt=\"Items Reworked Preview 1\" width=\"500\"> <img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/null/description_9dac58bd-5eab-428e-b01d-b02e567c3a54.jpg\" alt=\"Items Reworked Preview 2\" width=\"500\" height=\"339\"> <img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/null/description_ba4f84e1-af69-4b34-bc58-d83fcc4cd408.jpg\" alt=\"Items Reworked Preview 3\" width=\"500\" height=\"337\"></p>",
